{"word":"χρεώ","slug":"χρεώ","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n114592\" key=\"xrew/\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">χρεώ</orth>, <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ep.\">Ep.</a></gram> </gramGrp> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">χρειώ</orth>, gen. <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">οῦς</itype>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ἡ</gen>, less freq. neut., <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:10:142\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">10.142</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:2:28\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.28</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:5:189\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.189</biblScope> </bibl> (where <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τόσον</foreign> agrees with <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">χ.</foreign>), <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:4:312\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.312</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:10:85\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">10.85</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:11:606\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">11.606</biblScope></bibl>, perh. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:9:197\" defau